{"tid":1174780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首屆「太平洋先鋒」聯演 美日韓澳加強合作","createTime":"2019-05-28T05:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T10:31:00.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"11c9756cd42d3a042ec6e434f689cd10be47320f","tid":1174780,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:43:40.000Z","msg":"首屆「太平洋先鋒」聯演 美日韓澳加強合作<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%96%E5%B1%86-%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B4%8B%E5%85%88%E9%8B%92-%E8%81%AF%E6%BC%94-%E7%BE%8E%E6%97%A5%E9%9F%93%E6%BE%B3%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-160000774.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25B1%2586-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B4%258B%25E5%2585%2588%25E9%258B%2592-%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%25BC%2594-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%259F%2593%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C-160000774.html&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQbtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=fba20299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%96%E5%B1%86-%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B4%8B%E5%85%88%E9%8B%92-%E8%81%AF%E6%BC%94-%E7%BE%8E%E6%97%A5%E9%9F%93%E6%BE%B3%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-160000774.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美軍《星條旗報》26日表示，美國、日本、南韓、澳洲正於關島附近舉行首屆「太平洋先鋒」（Pacific Vanguard）聯合演習，總參演人數逾3000人，希望加強各國於印太區域的軍事合作。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>演練防空、反艦、反潛作戰</strong><br />\n<br />\n「太平洋先鋒19-1」自23日持續至28日，進行防空、反艦、反潛等作戰課目，參演者包括美國海軍「藍嶺號」兩棲指揮艦（LCC 19）、「安提坦號」神盾巡洋艦（CG 54）、「韋伯號」神盾驅逐艦（DDG 54）、「拉帕漢諾克號」運油艦（T-AO 204）、「勃德號」彈藥補給艦（T-AKE 4）、日本海上自衛隊「有明號」（DD-109）與「朝日號」護衛艦（DD-119）、南韓海軍「王建號」驅逐艦（DDH-978），以及澳洲皇家海軍「墨爾本號」（FFG-05）、「帕拉馬塔號」（FFH-154）巡防艦和1艘柯林斯級潛艦。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>日韓罕見同台操演 仍見齟齬<br />\n</strong><br />\n由於歷史因素和領土糾紛，日本與南韓極少在軍事演習中「同台演出」，就算參演，也大多僅在搜救、人道救援等無關作戰的項目中合作；加上去年10月南韓要求欲參加國際觀艦式的海自艦艇不得懸掛「旭日旗」（自衛艦旗），12月南韓軍艦又以射控雷達鎖定日本巡邏機，導致雙方關係降至冰點。兩國此次同時參與聯演，可能是在美國要求下，表現共同對抗北韓、中共等對手的態度。不過日本外務省25日於官網解釋旭日旗在該國歷史與民間文化的地位，又遭南韓媒體猛烈批評，稱「未提及二戰戰犯日軍同樣使用該旗幟」。"},{"pid":"4e0bc9d5733c1508e47824c709e5f9b0e854344a","tid":1174780,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T06:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93ee2ed750e2dd3bf656c237b53eafbfcc5019b","tid":1174780,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31cf97b587026a63dfc76f1510e3c23d558ec09e","tid":1174780,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fabeed763c3bb35286f5a209bf6a57f82b924c5","tid":1174780,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}